OL,3,CStepping down was the 'right thing to
OL,4,Cdo personally', says PM
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has vowed to "go in
OL,7,Fgood grace", saying he intends to "do
OL,8,Feverything (he) can to make sure what
OL,9,Fhappens next is a success".
OL,11,FSpeaking to journalists at the Nato
OL,12,Fsummit in Turkey, Starmer said: "It
OL,13,Fmatters to me that the country
OL,14,Fthrives, and therefore not only do I
OL,15,Fthink it's the right thing to do
OL,16,Fpersonally for me, I genuinely think
OL,17,Fit's the right thing to do for the
OL,18,Fcountry."
