OL,3,CStepping down was the 'right thing to
OL,4,Cdo personally', says PM
OL,6,FHis trip to Ankara is Starmer's last
OL,7,Fappearance on the world stage and
OL,8,Fcomes as nominations for the Labour
OL,9,Fleadership contest opened, with Andy
OL,10,FBurnham widely expected to be the only
OL,11,Fcandidate.
OL,13,FCandidates require at least 81
OL,14,Fnominations from fellow MPs to stand,
OL,15,Fand with the withdrawal of Wes
OL,16,FStreeting, Darren Jones, and Al Carns,
OL,17,FBurnham's path to a coronation seems
OL,18,Fclear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
