OL,3,CStepping down was the 'right thing to
OL,4,Cdo personally', says PM
OL,6,FSpeaking on Wednesday, the PM spoke
OL,7,Fmore about his life after stepping
OL,8,Fdown as prime minister, saying he did
OL,9,Fnot intend to offer advice to his
OL,10,Fsuccessor once rejoining the
OL,11,Fbackbenches.
OL,13,F"This is something I believe in quite
OL,14,Fstrongly," he said. "When I stepped
OL,15,Fdown as director of public
OL,16,Fprosecutions, I told my successor I
OL,17,Fwouldn't be commenting on each of the
OL,18,Fdecisions that they made.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
