CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1783639110
OL,3,CStepping down was the 'right thing to
OL,4,Cdo personally', says PM
OL,6,F"And I haven't. I've never commented
OL,7,Fon an individual case or where a
OL,8,Fdecision has been taken, and I intend
OL,9,Fto adopt the same approach.
OL,11,F"There are plenty of people giving
OL,12,Fprime ministers advice who performed
OL,13,Fall sorts of roles for our country,
OL,14,Fbut I don't intend to add my voice to
OL,15,Fthose by giving advice to my
OL,16,Fsuccessor, when actually, the truth is
OL,17,Fnobody quite
OL,19,Fknows what the trade-offs are in the
OL,20,Froom, apart from the person actually
OL,21,Fmaking the decision."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
