OL,3,CStepping down was the 'right thing to
OL,4,Cdo personally', says PM
OL,6,FEchoing the words of his own
OL,7,Fresignation speech, Starmer said the
OL,8,Fanswer to the question of who was best
OL,9,Fplaced to turn his party around and
OL,10,Fsecure a landslide victory at the 2024
OL,11,Felection "has been answered".
OL,13,FHe added, however, "the question my
OL,14,FMPs, our parliamentary party, is
OL,15,Fasking now is, 'who's the right person
OL,16,Fto take us into the next election?'
OL,17,FThey've given their answer to that,
OL,18,Fand I accept it."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
