OL,3,CStepping down was the 'right thing to
OL,4,Cdo personally', says PM
OL,6,FPosting to social media, Burnham said
OL,7,Fhe had nominated himself to be leader
OL,8,Fof the Labour Party on Thursday,
OL,9,Fconfirming he was currently the only
OL,10,Fcandidate.
OL,12,F"The nomination process has opened
OL,13,Fthis morning, so glad to see some MPs
OL,14,Fgoing in," he joked.
OL,16,F"We'll get the first indication about
OL,17,F7pm tonight of the first number of MPs
OL,18,Fto sign up," he said, adding, "it's
OL,19,Fall starting to feel very real".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
