OL,3,CStepping down was the 'right thing to
OL,4,Cdo personally', says PM
OL,6,FAhead of nominating himself, Burnham
OL,7,Fhad written to Labour MPs promising to
OL,8,Freform the whipping system and value
OL,9,F"every member" of the parliamentary
OL,10,FLabour Party.
OL,12,FThe potential successor to Starmer
OL,13,Falso hinted he would make himself more
OL,14,Favailable to backbench MPs, something
OL,15,Fthe current PM has at times faced
OL,16,Fcriticism for failing to do.
